    "description": "你想伤害自己，玩小魔方之旅<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715290/extras/68c3b16e82ae5c52688a920b09cbd070.poster.avif?t=1629961924\" width=774 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715290/extras/68c3b16e82ae5c52688a920b09cbd070.webm?t=1629961924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715290/extras/68c3b16e82ae5c52688a920b09cbd070.mp4?t=1629961924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Little cube trip 是一款会让你流汗的硬核平台游戏。如果你完成了这个游戏，它不会让你无动于衷。情节在程序代码的世界中发展，立方体开始了它的旅程。小方块能打败敌人到达终点吗？<br>- 每个级别都充满了可怕的怪物和陷阱，威胁着早死的小立方体。<br>- 30 个对您来说并不容易的不同级别，每个级别都需要自己的方法。<br>- 不错的球员运动机制，不会在最重要的时刻离开你。<br>- 美丽的体素立方体图形。<br>- 不寻常的游戏玩法。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715290/extras/1a371d630740ad8277fa8d3eafe1a65b.avif?t=1629961924\" width=648 height=364 /></span><br>小心和警惕，游戏比看起来更难。",
